ns the cooke driefontein and kloof operations in the west witwatersrand region and the beatrix operation in the southern free state province in addition to its mining activities sibanye owns and manages extraction and processing facilities at the operations where the goldbearing ore is treated the company has various organic projects including the kloof and driefontein below infrastructure projects on the west rand and the burnstone project on the south rand of gauteng province sibanye mines extracts and processes gold ore to produce a product dore sibanye derives uranium ore as a byproduct of gold production from the cooke operation more from reuters » officers and directors neal john froneman chief executive officer executive director age  bio  compensation   reuters charl keyter chief financial officer executive director age  bio  compensation   reuters wayne robinson chief executive officer  gold and uranium division age  bio  compensation   reuters christopher bateman executive vice president  us region age  bio  compensation   reuters hartley dikgale executive vice president  corporate affairs age  bio  compensation   reuters dawid j mostert executive vice president  commercial service age  bio  compensation   reuters richard a stewart executive vice president  business development age  bio  compensation   reuters robert van niekerk chief executive office  platinum division executive vice president age  bio  compensation   reuters john wallington executive vice president  coal and energy age  bio  compensation   reuters james r wellsted senior vice president  investor relations age  bio  compensation   reuters full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service sibanye gold  