f and driefontein below infrastructure projects on the west rand and the burnstone project on the south rand of gauteng province sibanye mines extracts and processes gold ore to produce a product dore sibanye derives uranium ore as a byproduct of gold production from the cooke operation industry sector and symbol sector na industry na subindustry na symbol jsesgl cusip na web wwwsibanyegoldcoza average prices day moving avg  day moving avg  petrailing pe ratio nape growth  profitabilitynet margins return on equity return on assets    frequently asked questions for sibanye gold ltd jsesgl what is sibanye gold ltds stock symbol sibanye gold ltd trades on the jse under the ticker symbol sgl who are sibanye gold ltds key executives sibanye gold ltds management team includes the folowing people neal john froneman chief executive officer executive directorcharl keyter chief financial officer executive directorwayne robinson chief executive officer  gold and uranium divisionrobert van niekerk chief executive office  platinum divisionchristopher bateman executive vice president  us regionhartley dikgale executive vice president  corporate affairsdawid j mostert executive vice president  commercial servicerichard a stewart executive vice president  business developmentjohn wallington executive vice president  coal and energyjames r wellsted senior vice president  investor relations how do i buy sibanye gold ltd stock shares of sibanye gold ltd can be purchased through any online brokerage account popular online brokerages include vanguard brokerage services td ameritrade etrade scottrade fidelity and charles schwab marketbeat community rating for sibanye gold ltd jse sglcommunity ranking   out of   outperform votes   vote outperformunderperform votes   vote underperformtotal votes  marketbeats community ratings are surveys of what our community members think about sibanye gold ltd and other stocks vote outperform if you believe the stock will outperform the sp  over the long term vote underperform if you believe the stock will underperform the sp  over the long term you may vote once every thirty days analyst ratings consensus ratings for sibanye gold ltd jsesgl how are consensus ratings calculated marketbeat calculates consensus ratings using the most recent rating from each brokerage that has rated a stock within the last twelve months since brokers often use different ratings systems each rating is normalized to a standardized rating score of  sell  hold  buy or  strong buy consensus ratings scores are calculated using the mean average of the number of normalized sell hold buy and strong buy ratings each stocks consensus rating is derived from its calculated consensus ratings score   sell   hold   buy   strong buy marketbeats consensus price targets are a mean average of the most recent available price targets set by each analyst that has set a price target for the stock in the last twelve monthsmarketbeat will no longer include ratings and price target data in its consensus calculation if a broker drops coverage and marketbeat has received a report that coverage was dropped ratings from certain research firms that issue ratings using purely quantitative methods such as zacks vetr and valuengine are not included in consensus calculations marketbeats consensus ratings and consensus price targets may differ from those calculated by other firms due to differences in methodology and available dataratings breakdown no ratings tracked in the last  monthsconsensus ratingna score nanconsensus price target na analysts ratings history for sibanye gold ltd jsesgl show only the most recent rating from each brokerage all ratings for this stock datefirmactionratingprice targetdetailsroyal bank of canadainitiated coveragesector performdata available from  forward earnings earnings history for sibanye gold ltd jsesglno earnings announcements for this company have been tracked by marketbeatcom estimates earnings estimates for sibanye gold ltd jsesgl