rganic projects including the kloof and driefontein below infrastructure projects on the west rand and the burnstone project on the south rand of gauteng province sibanye mines extracts and processes gold ore to produce a product dore sibanye derives uranium ore as a byproduct of gold production from the cooke operation receive news  ratings via email  enter your email address below to receive a concise daily summary of the latest news and analysts ratings with marketbeatcoms free daily email newsletter leave a reply cancel reply your email address will not be published required fields are marked comment name  email  website more news teekay offshore nysetoo has been downgraded from outperform to mkt perform in a statement by raymond james earlier today raymond james has downgraded teekay offshore microstrategy nasdaqmstr stock price target reduced to  issued a research note today by deutsche bank boasting a price of  microstrategy apptio nasdaqapti target price raised to  issued a report today by oppenheimer only yesterday apptio nasdaqapti traded  citigroup downgraded us steel nysex from neutral to sell in a report released today boasting a price of  us walmart stores inc nysewmt target price raised to  issued a report today by zacks investment research yesterday walmart stores inc nysewmt traded wolseley plc adr nasdaqwosyy target price raised to  issued a report today by zacks investment research yesterday wolseley plc adr nasdaqwosyy traded columbus mckinnon nasdaqcmco target price raised to  reported today by roth capital columbus mckinnon nasdaqcmco had its target starbucks nasdaqsbux has been downgraded from buy to neutral in a statement by guggenheim earlier today guggenheim has downgraded starbucks nasdaqsbux from zacks investment research disclosed wpp plc – american depositary shares each representing five ordinary shares nasdaqwppgy boosting its price target to  earlier today reporting a potential upside of  spirit airlines nasdaqsave has been downgrade