g rights covering a total of over  hectares it is an underground mine with surface reserves represented by rock dumps and tailings storage facility tsfs driefontein has approximately six operating shaft systems at depths of between  meters and  meters below surface and over three metallurgical plants exploiting the carbon leader reef the ventersdorp contact reef and the middelvlei reef the driefontein  plant treats underground ore and has a processing capacity of over  total productive maintenance tpm the upgraded cip circuit at the no  plant consists of a semiautogenous grinding sag mill circuit followed by cyanide leaching carboninpulp cip and a central elution facility the driefontein  plant processes surface rock dumps srd material which is delivered by rail and truck plant flow incorporates over two sag mills and a ball milling circuit cyanide leaching and a cip plant the driefontein  plant has over four sag mills followed by cyanide leaching and a cip circuitkloofkloof is located in the far west rand mining district of westonaria approximately  kilometers southwest of johannesburg in gauteng province south africa kloofs mining rights cover a total of approximately  hectares it is principally an underground mine with nominal surface reserves represented by srds and tsfs accumulated during the operating history of the mine the kloof operation is a complex of intermediate to ultradeep level mines predominantly mining the ventersdorp contact reef at depths of between  meters and  meters below surface the mine is situated near regional urban centers where it can routinely obtain supplies kloofs operations comprise over five producing shaft systems and approximately two metallurgical gold plants the kloof  plant kp comprises threestage crushing opencircuit rod mills for primary grinding and closedcircuit pebble mills for secondary milling this is followed by cyanide leaching filtration zinc precipitation and smelting the kloof  plant kp treats all of kloofs underground ore reef is trucked and conveyed to a central stacker pad which feeds over two sag mills equipped with variablespeed ring motor drives cyanide leaching cip and treatment at an independent elution and smelting facility follow millingbeatrixbeatrix is located in the free state province of south africa approximately  kilometers southwest of johannesburg near welkom and virginia covering a total area of over  hectares beatrix is principally an underground mine with nominal surface reserves represented by srds accumulated during the operating history of the mine beatrix has approximately three operating shaft systems with over two ventilation shafts to provide additional upcast and downcast ventilation capacity beatrix is a shallow to intermediatedepth operation mining at depths of between  meters and  meters below surface exploits the beatrix reef at shafts  and  and the kalkoenkrans reef at  shaft situated near regional urban centers where it can routinely obtain supplies the mine has access to the national electricity grid and to water road and rail infrastructurecookethe cooke mine is located near randfontein southwest of johannesburg in the province of gauteng south africa the cooke underground operations comprise over four vertical shafts cooke  to  and the ezulwini plant as well as the surface operation which are serviced by a network of mining and civil infrastructure the operations have over three individual new order mining rights cooke   and  cover over  hectares cooke  covers approximately  hectares and the surface operations cover over  hectares the primary goldbearing reef horizon mined at cooke   and  is the uea and the upper elsburg reef at cooke  » full overview of sbgln company address sibanye gold ltd libanon business park hospital road off cedar avenuwestonaria      p  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation matthews moloko  neal froneman  charl keyter  wayne robinson  christopher bateman  » more officers  directors siban